# Add the following modules to the setup flow

1. **cargo crate `cargo-update`**  
   Designed to simplify updating system cargo crates.

2. **uv tool install:**  
   - `netron`
   - `smashh`
   - `gdown`
   - `"huggingface_hub[cli]"`
   - To install `hf_transfer`, do this:

     ```bash
     source ~/.local/share/uv/tools/huggingface-hub/bin/activate
     uv pip install hf_transfer
     deactivate
     ```

3. **go install:**
   - `github.com/charmbracelet/mods@latest`
   - `github.com/charmbracelet/gum@latest`
   - `github.com/charmbracelet/glow@latest`
   - `github.com/jorgerojas26/lazysql@latest`

4. **Install `iperf3`**

5. **Install GitHub CLI and GitLab CLI**

6. **Install lazygit as follows:**

   ```bash
   LAZYGIT_VERSION=$(curl -s "https://api.github.com/repos/jesseduffield/lazygit/releases/latest" | grep -Po '"tag_name": *"v\K[^"]*')
   curl -Lo lazygit.tar.gz "https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/releases/download/v${LAZYGIT_VERSION}/lazygit_${LAZYGIT_VERSION}_Linux_x86_64.tar.gz"
   tar xf lazygit.tar.gz lazygit
   sudo install lazygit -D -t /usr/local/bin/
   ```
